@startuml UC12_Sequence
title UC12: 发布课程信息 - 顺序图

actor "教务处" as AA
boundary "课程详情编辑界面" as EditForm
control "课程控制器" as CourseCtrl
entity "Course" as Course

AA -> EditForm : 补充大纲、计划、教材等内容
EditForm -> CourseCtrl : publishCourseInfo(courseId, details)
CourseCtrl -> Course : updateDetails(details)
Course --> CourseCtrl : success
CourseCtrl --> AA : 提示发布成功
@enduml
